description:
On today’s throwback podcast from the SWE Vault, Dr. Emily is joined by Menace and they’re getting into everything oral sex – from oral etiquette to getting over insecurities – and she’s answering your questions. 

The two discuss the craziest places they’ve had oral, as well as the way social media is taking a toll on relationships (mind you, this was 3 years ago!). Plus, Emily gives advice on getting past the gag reflex, confusion on your partner’s oral reactions, and details on going from front to back (hint: don’t!).


Follow Emily on all social: @sexwithemily

Follow Menace on all social: @menace

For even more sex advice, tips, & tricks, visit sexwithemily.com


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
